The '''flag of North Holland''' ({{lang-nl|vlag van Noord-Holland}}) is the official [[flag]] of [[North Holland]]. The flag was adopted on 22 October 1958 after it was approved by the [[Hoge Raad van Adel]]. The colours originate from the [[coat of arms of North Holland]].<ref>{{nl icon}} Provincie Noord-Holland (2007): [http://www.noord-holland.nl/thema/concern/Over_Noord_Holland/Historie/vlag_en_wapen.asp?thema=home&ComponentID=62018&SourcePageID=57379#62018 Over Noord-Holland - Historie]</ref>

