===FSF 2018 Shadow Bank OFC list===

Shadow banking is a key service line for OFCs.  The Financial Stability Forum ("FSF") produces a report each year on ''Global Shadow Banking'', or ''other financial intermediaries'' ("OFI"s){{efn|name=OFI}}.  In a similar method to the various IMF lists, the FSF produces a table of the locations with the highest concentration of OFI/shadow banking financial assets, versus domestic GDP, in its 2018 report, thus creating a ranked table of "Shadow Banking OFCs".<ref name="FSF1"/>  The fuller table is produced in the {{slink|#Shadow banking}} section, however, the 4 largest OFCs for shadow banking with OFI assets over 5x GDP are:<ref name="FSF1"/>

{{ordered list|

