'''Xaxaba Airfield''' {{Airport codes||FBXB}} is an [[airstrip]] {{convert|3.5|km}} west of [[Xaxaba]], a village in the [[Okavango Delta]] of [[Botswana]]. It serves several safari camps in the area. The runway is just outside the [[Moremi Game Reserve]].
