'''''Ärzte-Zeitung''''' (company name: '''''Ärzte Zeitung Verlags-GmbH''''': {{ISSN|0175-5811}}, [[Zeitschriftendatenbank|ZDB]] ([[:de:Zeitschriftendatenbank|DE]]) 604874-2) is a German newspaper for physicians and other medical professionals.<ref name=sprin>{{cite web|title=Ärzte Zeitung Verlags-GmbH|url=https://www.springer.com/gp/about-springer/company-information/locations/aerzte-zeitung-verlags-gmbh|work=Springer|accessdate=30 May 2015}}</ref> The paper was first published on 1 October 1982.<ref>{{cite news|title='Ärzte Zeitung' feiert 30-jähriges Jubiläum|url=http://www.healthcaremarketing.eu/medien/detail.php?nr=12786&rubric=Medien&|accessdate=30 May 2015|work=Healthcare Marketing|date=12 January 2012}}</ref> It is published by [[Springer Medizin]].<ref name=sprin/> The publication's head office is in [[Neu-Isenburg]].<ref>"[http://www.aerztezeitung.de/service/impressum/ Impressum]." ''Ärzte-Zeitung''. Retrieved on 4 April 2015. "Ärzte Zeitung Verlags-GmbH Am Forsthaus Gravenbruch 5 63263 Neu-Isenburg"</ref>

